## Anti-Rationalization

| Rationalization | Reality |
|-----------------|---------|
| "Close enough" on quotes | Preserve exact wording |
| "Skip old meetings" | Process all in time window |
| "This signal doesn't fit" | Categorize best match or flag |
| "I remember an older version" | Use current data only |
